<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">David James Duncan</span></strong> is a renowned fly fisherman and the author of several books, including the novel <em>The River Why</em> (Sierra Club Books) and the nonfiction collection <em>My God Laughs &amp; Plays</em> (Triad Books). He lives in Montana and is at work on a novel that attempts to reconcile his western boots and Eastern books, titled <em>Eastern Western</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/david-james-duncan" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

